data.text: @shaykhouston_ She gave me a pretty strong Pisces vibe because of how reserved and mysterious she is. Also, most Pisces tend to be artistic, and she has that paper art business she runs on the side with her modeling career.

@IceColdKilla9 Lol I know! I’m a Capricorn, but I have an Aries moon. I’m way more Aries-like than she is. Even most Pisces, that I know, have more personality than that. I don’t even think it could be blamed on being introverted. She’s just dull. 😕😂

@shaykhouston_ It’s hilarious that she’s an Aries. Fire signs are extroverted and totally in your face, which is the complete opposite of what we’re seeing of her 😂

She strikes me as more of a Pisces tbh. I’m pretty sure she’s in the Pisces cusp with her late March birthday.
